snippet.textDisplay: After watching the sequel trilogy I realized J.J. should’ve produced all three films. With the different visions that Ryan had it was like J.J. had to go back in TROS and explain everything that could’ve been detailed a lot more. I still love this trilogy it’s just things that you notice a lot and go why didn’t they just stick with that and make a lot more sense? In the end I loved TROS and the characters of this trilogy are amazing but the story really is just everywhere.
